{"tid":2081861,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"張崑陽：我係一個本土派","createTime":"2020-06-27T14:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T13:57:01.000Z","uid":51992,"like":20,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe1970c173646a30b6ecf3d940fc0cb83554790","tid":2081861,"uid":51992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第一屆本土學生會莊</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2015年張崑陽成功當選為浸大學生會外務副幹事長。<span style=\"color: red;\">該屆學生會響應本土思潮，是首間表明不參加維園六四燭光晚會的大學學生會。時任學聯常委的張崑陽主張退出晚會，強調雖然六四晚會有其意義，亦啟蒙了很多年輕人，但晚會只停留在哀傷層面而沒有抗爭。</span><br />\n<br />\n張崑陽表示六四晚會口號之一的「建設民主中國」不應是香港這一代人的責任，質疑香港是否能分身再去處理中國的民主訴求。由於根據學聯的共識制，出席六四晚會需要所有學生會全體一致通過議案，只要一間院校反對，便不能以學聯的名義行動，故此該年亦是學聯26年來首次不以聯會名義出席晚會。 <br />\n<br />\nFrom wiki<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">本土派認證</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7PCBa2S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7PCBa2S.jpg&h=bebddbcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴治奧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFrm6CG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFrm6CG.png&h=e3a46d9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n「在這個時代參選，猶如『報名坐監』」「在屈辱和戰爭之間，即使選擇了屈辱，最後也得面對戰爭。」「有很多年輕人，在時代革命裏展現了無比勇氣，用搏命的決心，打好每一條戰線，我相信不論是Sunny、Lester還是阿藍，也能做到這一點。我希望香港人在民主派初選，以及九月的立法會選舉支持他們。」&mdash;&mdash;梁頌恆</span>"},{"pid":"82a9dcf2bfec125c0ca216464cb3e0743c3688ff","tid":2081861,"uid":51992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f26b4c7cb4f2ea42285c2eea6879cb480bef9d","tid":2081861,"uid":51992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8206a0c2913a37554a86b0c31056141e5caad6","tid":2081861,"uid":51992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6450440b22bb36aa29e0d78e1ac62949d6d9d3","tid":2081861,"uid":51992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c208a9cc2fa09d5b616010bca86f3879657c55a","tid":2081861,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:32:18.000Z","msg":"本土，俾人DQ機會高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee1fc09d95278642ce60bff0dd67ca7ce3f9f57","tid":2081861,"uid":51992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c208a9cc2fa09d5b616010bca86f3879657c55a","tid":2081861,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:32:18.000Z","msg":"本土，俾人DQ機會高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:35:01.000Z","msg":"所以初選要投票，打國際線需要民意授權"},{"pid":"0ff524649e481645542b5308ce88783ecca93c6c","tid":2081861,"uid":51992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb84dc75ee3b49ed954c3986aca6bfb51898c97","tid":2081861,"uid":51992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088bf964ec421db62c8b95ff77da27ea1dac04b6","tid":2081861,"uid":51992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840a7dc4a221abcc3ae538f2cd14675707a5e9b1","tid":2081861,"uid":295650,